Introduction

Kaede is a Japanese dancer, singer, and rapper under MODHAUS.

On November 9, 2022, Kaede was introduced as the ninth member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. She made her debut with the first ten members of the group on February 13, 2023, with the mini album "ASSEMBLE".

As a member of tripleS, Kaede was placed in the sub-units LOVElution, Aria, and Visionary Vision.
